{"tid":755384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑回抽：贊成停課是承認自己種族低劣弱雞","createTime":"2018-07-25T07:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T12:06:53.000Z","uid":19552,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ae40691a38788332f63576fdbee3823224e6f7","tid":755384,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:21:45.000Z","msg":"如此天氣，贊成要停課的，必是弱者。而根據達爾文定律：弱者應該淘汰。 <br />\n<br />\n有人說：日本北歐的課室有暖氣。但那裡的天氣有幾個月的真正寒冬，年年下雪，時時零下。香港偶爾一兩日三五度，香港的課室冇暖氣，D小朋友絕對不會凍死。我受你「三度凍死保險」。 <br />\n<br />\n如果話：不可以將香港中國小朋友的體質與北方國家兒童相比。香港兒童三度攝氏會患「低溫症」。 <br />\n<br />\n什麼叫「低溫症」？有一兩個小朋友凍到病，由佢病吧。小孩係由小病小痛學會免疫。三十三度，一樣有學童中暑暈低，為什麼不全港停課？ <br />\n<br />\n有人話：不可以將香港兒童體質同北歐日本比。咁就更好笑：你承認華南兒童體質天生潺弱，豈不是承認本身種族低劣？係咪宣傳種族主義法西斯？老老實實，一個連攝氏三度都嚇到視為世界末日的民族，在這個星球，遲早會淘汰。 <br />\n<br />\n西方有一種教育，叫「斯巴達教育」。前英殖留給香港的毅行者外展活動、童軍，唔知學的是什麼？ <br />\n<br />\n唔習慣？以後天氣年年反常，現在開始習慣得唔得？攝氏三度都視為畏途，中國山西和東北的小學生，一定強過你，弱雞如此，請問香港又點樣「本土」，又有什麼能力「港獨」？"},{"pid":"7a9b1750b60f0a28638e5021da396fce6f12d3d6","tid":755384,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"日本唔係停課<br />\n係延長暑假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22d30071fbdb21ed77d65d598f67724ec7df7de","tid":755384,"uid":117856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140123005282-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20140123005282-260408&d=FWxduykNtOOU8L%2FspW3vaAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=17514a9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140123005282-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n秦國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a6fd95483e390d7255a3956a9f56c19af7a37e","tid":755384,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"反對停課唔係問題<br />\n但係用返「唔捱得」呢啲咁低質嘅論據<br />\n陶傑有冇低能咗啲"},{"pid":"bcdd64fb9c98b4f9faaefec019aed0bacc4df91c","tid":755384,"uid":193407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"扯到去種族低劣好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境唔一樣點比啊大佬 人地冬天平均幾度我地冬天平均幾度啊<br />\n唔係話支持停課 而係扯到去自尊嚟令人認同自己真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df118761f8dbfa8c134867380c4f172cec8dffc3","tid":755384,"uid":182864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9a6fd95483e390d7255a3956a9f56c19af7a37e","tid":755384,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"反對停課唔係問題<br />\n但係用返「唔捱得」呢啲咁低質嘅論據<br />\n陶傑有冇低能咗啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:29:07.000Z","msg":"反觀個班話要停課個班就好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a597e36fdc1d838c9c976cce190083ae3de3a091","tid":755384,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df118761f8dbfa8c134867380c4f172cec8dffc3","tid":755384,"uid":182864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9a6fd95483e390d7255a3956a9f56c19af7a37e","tid":755384,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"反對停課唔係問題<br />\n但係用返「唔捱得」呢啲咁低質嘅論據<br />\n陶傑有冇低能咗啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:29:07.000Z","msg":"反觀個班話要停課個班就好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"冇講過<br />\n唔好兩立化件事"},{"pid":"3121b6ee21409b5663c2fd6e11b9d759f13ff434","tid":755384,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"986e7ffc1dcb1ff64a0ff537bf1e011521ec17e6","tid":755384,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"19今次想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi